title: Blue d'hide trimmed armour

properties.name: description
properties.value: Blue d'hide trimmed armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Blue d'hide armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from hard Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.

content:
A player wearing trimmed blue dragonhide armour.

Blue d'hide trimmed armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Blue d'hide armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from hard Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.
